"*Naučio* sam da čitam i pišem (I learned to read and write).

"*Naučila* je da sama obavlja računarske zadatke (She learned to do computer tasks by herself).

"*Naučiti* će te da koristiš računar (You will learn to use the computer).

"*Naučen* je da se izražava jasno i tačno (He was taught to express himself clearly and accurately).

"On je *naučio* da kuva mnogo ukusnih jela (He learned to cook many delicious dishes).